'''瑪格·艾麗絲·羅比'''（{{lang-en|Margot Elise Robbie}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fosters.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20110822/GJNEWS_01/708229958/-1/FOSNEWS|title=Marketing the world's most experienced airline: Dover business works to keep Pan Am brand alive|last=Ramsdell|first=Laurenne|work=[[Foster's_Daily_Democrat|Foster's Daily Democrat]]|date=22 August 2011|accessdate=12 January 2014|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201010526/https://www.fosters.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20110822%2FGJNEWS_01%2F708229958%2F-1%2FFOSNEWS|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{bd|1990年|7月2日|catIdx=R}}）是一位[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]女[[演员|演员]]。早期主要出演電視劇，包括《[[泛美之旅|泛美之旅]]》（2011年-2012年）等。後來往電影方面發展，其中她在《[[华尔街之狼|华尔街之狼]]》（2013年）的演出為她帶來多項獎項提名<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2592856/Margot-Robbie-stuns-scarlet-red-gown-leads-way-winners-Empire-Film-Awards.html "'I've never won an award before': Margot Robbie stuns in scarlet red gown as she leads the winners at the Empire Film Awards"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2592856/Margot-Robbie-stuns-scarlet-red-gown-leads-way-winners-Empire-Film-Awards.html |date=20160828010511 }}, DailyMail, 30 May, 2014.</ref>。2014年，羅比被提名[[好萊塢青年獎|好萊塢青年獎突破演出女星]]；隔年，她獲得[[英国电影学院奖新星奖|英国电影学院奖新星奖]]提名。

2016年，她在超級英雄電影《[[自殺突擊隊_(電影)|自殺突擊隊]]》中飾演[[小丑女|小丑女]]一角而名聲大噪，雖然影評不佳，但票房收入是當年當月最高。2017年，羅比在《[[老娘叫譚雅|老娘叫譚雅]]》中主演[[譚雅·哈丁|譚雅·哈丁]]一角使她獲得多個影評人協會獎項的認同，亦令她首次獲得[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]、[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]和[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]等四大獎項獎項女主角之提名。
2019年，與[[李奧納多·狄卡皮歐|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]及[[布萊德·彼特|布萊德·彼特]]合作出演的《[[從前，有個好萊塢|從前，有個好萊塢]]》獲得廣大好評外也在各大影評協會入圍和贏得許多獎項，隨後又以《[[重磅腥聞|重磅腥聞]]》入圍[[第77屆金球獎|第77屆金球獎]]劇情類、音樂及喜劇類最佳女配角以及[[第92屆奧斯卡金像獎|第92屆奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳女配角。

== 早期生活 ==
羅比出生於[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]][[多爾比_(昆士蘭州)|多爾比]]的[[黃金海岸_(澳洲)|黃金海岸]]，與她的祖父母在農場中生活。當她十七歲時，她搬到了[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]，並開始演藝事業<ref name="LCB">{{cite web|url=http://beta.abc.go.com/shows/pan-am/bios/laura-cameron|title=Laura Cameron Bio|publisher=[[American_Broadcasting_Company|American Broadcasting Company]]|accessdate=27 September 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926094315/http://beta.abc.go.com/shows/pan-am/bios/laura-cameron|archivedate=2011-09-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2007年，她從位於黃金海岸的[[薩默塞特學院|薩默塞特學院]]畢業<ref name="Miller">{{cite web|url=http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2009/04/14/68845_gossip-news.html|title=Margot Robbie still girl next door|last=Miller|first=Katie|date=14 April 2009|publisher=Gold Coast|accessdate=6 March 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925123847/http://www.goldcoast.com.au/article/2009/04/14/68845_gossip-news.html|archivedate=2009-09-25|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
2009年，羅比開始和《家有芳鄰》的女演員[[艾什利·布魯爾|艾什利·布魯爾]]一同生活<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25482487-5003422,00.html|title=Teenager Ashleigh Brewer lands part with Neighbours|work=[[The_Courier-Mail|The Courier-Mail]]|publisher=[[Queensland_Newspapers|Queensland Newspapers]]|date=15 May 2009|first=Geoff|last=Shearer|accessdate=4 August 2010|archive-date=2009-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090525163910/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25482487-5003422,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當她退出《家有芳鄰》後，她宣布搬至[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]與[[凱特琳·史泰西|凱特琳·史泰西]]一起住。羅比在出演《泛美之旅》時則住在[[紐約|紐約]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/soaps/s14/neighbours/news/a285935/neighbours-star-reveals-hollywood-plans.html|title='Neighbours' star reveals Hollywood plans|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|publisher=Hachette Filipacchi UK|date=4 November 2010|first=Daniel|last=Kilkelly|accessdate=4 November 2010|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190937/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/soaps/s14/neighbours/news/a285935/neighbours-star-reveals-hollywood-plans.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自2014年起，羅比一直與英國副導湯姆·艾克禮（Tom Ackerley）交往<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/573971/margot-robbie-plants-a-fat-kiss-on-new-boyfriend-tom-ackerley-see-the-sweet-pics|title=Margot Robbie Plants a Fat Kiss on New Boyfriend Tom Ackerley—See the Sweet Pics!|last=Nessif|first=Bruna|date=27 August 2014|publisher=[[E!|E!]]|accessdate=4 August 2015|archivedate=2015-08-04|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6aXEqCJKd?url=http://www.eonline.com/news/573971/margot-robbie-plants-a-fat-kiss-on-new-boyfriend-tom-ackerley-see-the-sweet-pics|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.couriermail.com.au/entertainment/confidential/margot-robbie-confirms-relationship-with-tom-ackerly-still-going-strong/story-fnn7l51k-1227240564128|title=Margot Robbie confirms relationship with Tom Ackerly still going strong|last=Molloy|first=Shannon|date=27 February 2015|work=[[The_Courier-Mail|The Courier-Mail]]|location=[[Brisbane,_Australia|Brisbane, Australia]]|accessdate=28 February 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309130929/http://www.couriermail.com.au/entertainment/confidential/margot-robbie-confirms-relationship-with-tom-ackerly-still-going-strong/story-fnn7l51k-1227240564128 | archivedate=9 March 2015|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2016年12月，她與艾克禮在[[拜倫灣|拜倫灣]]低調地舉行私人婚禮<ref name="Selleck">{{cite news|url=http://www.goldcoastbulletin.com.au/entertainment/suicide-squad-star-margot-robbie-and-director-tom-ackerley-marry-in-secret-ceremony-in-byron-bay/news-story/6669944e097c2cfeb406f8d72a6611e7?nk=cfb429b18655ca0e93ccfee99540e4e4-1482197887|title=Suicide Squad star Margot Robbie and director Tom Ackerley marry in secret ceremony in Byron Bay|last=Selleck|first=Emily|last2=Simonot|first2=Suzanne|date=19 December 2016|work=[[Gold_Coast_Bulletin|Gold Coast Bulletin]]|accessdate=20 December 2016|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701222658/https://www.goldcoastbulletin.com.au/entertainment/suicide-squad-star-margot-robbie-and-director-tom-ackerl